.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, software-developer, fisherman, musician, social-worker
House: cape-cod, futuristic, cottage, tower, victorian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
There 5 different types of food: mango, broccoli, pepper, zucchini, grapefruit
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, august, november, may, february
1. the cape-cod house is the fisherman
2. the swedish house is the person who's birthday is in november
3. the futuristic house is the person drinking tea
4. the software-developer is on the left of the musician
5. the software-developer is the person drinking coffee
6. the person eating pepper is the person who's birthday is in august
7. the social-worker is the person eating broccoli
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the tower house is on the far left
10. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september
11. the person who's birthday is in februarys is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli
12. the person eating mango is the person drinking beer
13. the cottage house is the person eating zucchini
14. the tower house is on the left or right of the dressmaker
15. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Job		|    social-worker	|     dressmaker	|      fisherman	|     software-developer	|     musician	|
| House	|   tower	|    futuristic	|    cape-cod	|    cottage	|    swedish	|
| Birthday		|     september	|    february	|     august	|     may	|      november	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Food		|   broccoli	|    grapefruit	|  pepper	|    zucchini	|   mango	|
